<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>David Warner is currently playing cricket for the Indian Premier League in the United Arab Emirates. </p>

<p>And between games he took some time out to reflect on his marriage with his wife Candice Warner, 35. </p>

<p>Posting to Instagram, the 33-year-old shared a throwback snap from their wedding and explained 'how lucky' he was to have her.   </p>

<p>'I truly am grateful!' On Tuesday, cricketer David Warner delivered a gushing tribute to his wife Candice (both pictured) as he reflected on the 'ups and downs' of their marriage </p>

<p>'When time flies, you sometimes forget to reflect on how lucky we are, especially when you look back at memories,' he wrote. </p>

<p>The sportsman explained that 'six years and three children later' he still loves to reminisce about all the reasons why he married his 'soul mate and best friend'.  </p>

<p>And while he admitted that the couple have experienced their fair share of 'laughter, tears, ups and downs', he is always 'grateful' to have Candice by his side. </p>

<p>Thankful: While David admitted that the couple have experienced their fair share of 'laughter, tears, ups and downs,' he is always 'grateful' to have Candice by his side</p>

<p>'Words will never be enough to describe what <?php echo e('@'); ?>candywarner1 means to me. I truly am grateful I have such a strong, determined, loving, caring wife.'  </p>

<p>It comes after he bid his three daughters a sweet farewell last month before departing to play cricket for the United Arab Emirates. </p>

<p>Posting to Instagram, David shared a sweet series of photos of his 'gorgeous girls' as they soaked up the sun in Sydney.</p>

<p>Fun in the sun: On Sunday, David Warner has gushed over his wife Candice and his three daughters Ivy Mae, five, and Indie Rae, four, and Isla, one, as they enjoyed a day out</p>

<p>'My gorgeous girls enjoying a great day out,' he wrote underneath a series of photos.</p>

<p>'Extremely blessed to have such a supportive, understanding, caring and loving wife,' he continued.</p>

<p>One photo sees Candice in a single sleeve red swimsuit, posing with daughters Ivy Mae, five, and Indie Rae, four, as she held onto baby Isla, one.</p>

<p>Sun day out: A second sees Ivy filling a bucket of sand, while she looked up at the camera.</p>

<p>A second sees Ivy filling a bucket of sand, while she looked up at the camera.</p>

<p>The third was a selfie of Candice and little Isla making the most of the sunny weather as they posed while sitting on the beach.</p>

<p>David and Candice were married in 2015 at Terrara House Estate winery on the New South Wales South Coast.</p>

